Babies make use of various feeding and other accessories during their growth period
column13:
which help them learn and develop into healthy individuals. Carrying wet wipes for babies during travelling will prove to be helpful for the mother as well as the baby. The Farlin Baby Wet Wipes are made to be Anti-Rash so that they tender gently and smoothly to the baby’s delicate skin.

This Farlin Baby Wet Wipes – Anti-Rash can suitably be used for both girls and boys. These wet wipes provide a feeling of freshness to the baby and prove to be appealing to the baby. These wet wipes come in a packet and are made to be Alcohol Free so that they do not cause any harmful side effects to the baby’s body. These wet wipes provide a soft and moisturising feeling to the baby’s body and free them from dryness and discomfort. These Farlin Baby Wet Wipes – Anti-Rash are made to be Fragrance Free and are available in a pack of 85 pieces.
